\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Toggles whether the space and time parts of the Lorentz transform are applied
 to the final display coordinates shown onscreen.
 With both off, all events are shown in world frame coordinates.
 With both on, the events are seen in the coordinates of the target particle;
